  "doc_id": "40650",
  "text": "Eqn. (3) is the famous \"law of the wall\", in which κ = 0.41 is the von Karman constant and B is a constant dependent on the roughness of solid walls. Based on these approximate solutions, Spalding [CITATION_1] proposed an empirical velocity function which has a good agreement with many experiments.",
